snippet.title: Bomb Chicken Nintendo Switch Trailer
snippet.description:
After a freak accident a seemingly ordinary chicken becomes a bomb laying free range hero!

Discover the darkest kept secret of the fast food giant known as BFC, their best selling addictive blue hot sauce, and answer the ultimate question: Which came first, the chicken or the bomb?

more info: http://bombchickengame.com/
